<br>
To the RP elite:<br>
<br>
My post was an attempt to give people who are unfamiliar with RP something to help them start off, since roleplay is endangered on FV. The &quot;you're not an RPer if you don't play MY way&quot; flames are taking their toll on me. Note that my guide never said there was one way to do anything. People are allowed to have their creative freedom to a certain extent, in my opinion, even if it is unorthodox. <br>
<br>
So, rather than continue to argue with the flippin RP elite, I'm going to throw in the towel. No, I don't roleplay *your* way, and many others don't as well. That doesn't mean their characters are any less valid, or that their way of thinking is any less warranted. <br>
<br>
But keep on snubbing people if that's what makes you feel good. <br>
<br>
